###

### Get all portfolios
GET {{host}}/api/portfolios

###

### Get a portfolios by ID
GET {{host}}/api/portfolios/1

###

### Update a portfolios
PUT {{host}}/api/portfolios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Project",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "sub_domain": "updated-sub",
  "theme": "dark",
  "layout": "list",
  "type": "biz"
}

###

### Delete a portfolios
DELETE {{host}}/api/portfolios/1

###

### Check a portfolios sub domain
GET {{host}}/api/portfolios/check/sub-domain/sebastech
